OL,6,FA haulage company has been fined
OL,7,F#85,000 after a fork lift truck driver
OL,8,Fwas killed at work as he loaded a
OL,9,Florry.
OL,11,FIan Dawson, 60, was putting pallets
OL,12,Fonto an HGV as it moved forward,
OL,13,Fcausing the fork lift truck to
OL,14,Foverturn.
