OL,6,FMr Dawson, from , who was not wearing
OL,7,Fa seatbelt, was trapped beneath the
OL,8,Fvehicle, and died as a result of his
OL,9,Finjuries in the incident on 19
OL,10,FNovember 2020, at Chorlton Express
OL,11,FTransport Limited in Royton, Greater
OL,12,FManchester.
OL,14,FHis partner, Jane Medhurst, described
OL,15,Fthe last moment she saw him, before
OL,16,Fthey both left for work on the day he
OL,17,Fdied.
