OL,6,FMs Medhurst said: "We told each other,
OL,7,F'love you', kissed and said, 'see you
OL,8,Flater'. What happened that day was so
OL,9,Fcatastrophic.
OL,11,F"It has drastically changed my life. I
OL,12,Fstill find it difficult to cope with
OL,13,Fthe loss of Ian.
OL,15,F"He loved his food and months after
OL,16,Fhis death I still found myself
OL,17,Fshopping for him.
OL,19,F"Thinking 'oh that's one of Ian's
OL,20,Ffavourites I will buy that'. Even
OL,21,Fthough I knew he was not here anymore.
