OL,6,F"Although I now realise Ian will never
OL,7,Fcome home again and I have now had to
OL,8,Fmove out of the house we shared, it
OL,9,Fstill haunts me that he is gone. It
OL,10,Fwas so sudden and unexpected that I
OL,11,Fnever got a chance to say goodbye to
OL,12,Fhim."
OL,14,FAn investigation by the Health and
OL,15,FSafety Executive (HSE) found Chorlton
OL,16,FExpress Transport Limited, based on
OL,17,FMeek Street, Royton, had failed to put
OL,18,Fin place sufficient safe systems of
OL,19,Fwork regarding vehicle movements.
