OL,6,FIt had also failed to ensure all fork
OL,7,Flift truck drivers were compelled to
OL,8,Fwear seatbelts.
OL,10,FManchester Magistrates Court heard had
OL,11,FMr Dawson been wearing a seatbelt, it
OL,12,Fis highly likely that this would have
OL,13,Fsaved his life.
OL,15,FHis daughter Caitlin, who was just 19
OL,16,Fwhen her dad died, said it had 'turned
OL,17,Fher life upside down'.
OL,19,FCaitlin said: "I can still remember
OL,20,Fgetting the phone call that my dad had
OL,21,Fpassed like it was yesterday.
