OL,6,F"At just 19 years old when it
OL,7,Fhappened, and it being the first time
OL,8,Flosing someone, it felt like my life
OL,9,Fhad turned upside down, especially in
OL,10,Fthe brutal terms it happened.
OL,12,F"To this day, I still sit and cry and
OL,13,Fthe fact that I will never get to say
OL,14,Fgoodbye to my dad. I will never be
OL,15,Fable to speak to him and he will never
OL,16,Fbe able to take me shopping again, one
OL,17,Fof the most fond memories I have of
OL,18,Fhim.
