OL,6,F"It has been one of the most
OL,7,Ftraumatising experiences of my life
OL,8,Fand I am still suffering every day
OL,9,Fbecause of it."
OL,11,FChorlton Express Transport Limited
OL,12,Fpleaded guilty to breaching
OL,13,Fregulations under the Health and
OL,14,FSafety at Work Act. It was fined
OL,15,F#86,710 and ordered to pay #5,903
OL,16,Fcosts at a hearing on 17 April.
OL,18,FThe prosecution was brought by HSE
OL,19,Fenforcement lawyer Matthew Reynolds
OL,20,Fand paralegal Lucy Gallagher.
