OL,6,FAfter the hearing HSE inspector Jane
OL,7,FCarroll said: "The failures of this
OL,8,Fcompany has left a family without the
OL,9,Fman they loved.
OL,11,F"The importance of wearing seatbelts
OL,12,Fcannot be stressed enough.
OL,14,F"The failures meant the company
OL,15,Fexposed employees, and others, to the
OL,16,Frisk of being struck or caught by
OL,17,Fworkplace vehicles.
